In Re Robert Lynn PRUETT, petitioner.
No. 17-6313 (17A391).
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 12, 2017.
Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO and by him to referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of habeas corpus denied.
